						<div class="postbody">BTW, I the Indiana Jones Last Crusade does 2 writes to $2006 to realign the scroll after the palette write. <s>This can only be done at a exactly divisible by 8 Y position.<br /><br />Therefore, to do more than 1 palette change would be spread out over &#40;8 * # of palette changes&#41; scanlines.<br /><br />&#40;# of palette changes, minus one, times 8&#41;</s></div>

					
